---
import Default from "@layouts/Default.astro";
---

<style>
  .bio {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 25% auto;
  }

  .bio div:not(div:first-child) {
    padding: 0 0 0 16px;
  }

  .bio img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 100%;
  }

  #bars {
    margin: 16px 0 2rem 0;
  }

  bar {
    padding: 8px;
    margin: 16px 0;
    display: block;
    min-height: 32px;
    background: var(--surface0);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  bar p {
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
  }

  bar fill {
    display: block;
    border-radius: 4px;
    min-height: 16px;
    /* TODO: Make gradient. */
    /* Or replace with GitHub language colors */
    background: var(--red);
  }

  @media only screen and (max-width: 800px) {
    .bio {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: auto;
    }

    .bio div:not(div:first-child) {
      padding: 0;
    }

    .bio div img {
      width: 50%;
      margin: 0 0 32px 0;
    }

    .bio div:first-child {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>

<Default pageTitle="About">
  <!-- TODO: Add picture next to my name -->
  <div class="bio">
    <div>
      <img
        src="https://github.com/ch3rries/ch3rries/raw/main/assets/StickersDoodle_cherry_rose.16b7d873.gif?raw=true"
        alt="Placeholder Image"
      />
    </div>
    <div>
      <h1>Hi, I'm Noah.</h1>
      <p>
        I'm a novice programmer with a love for making websites. I'm planning on
        working with frameworks in the future, this website may not stay the
        same for long.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <p style="margin-bottom: 0;">
    Anyway, here's my experience in some programming languages summed up:
  </p>

  <div id="bars">
    <bar>
      <p>HTML</p>
      <fill style="width: 90%;"></fill>
    </bar>
    <bar>
      <p>CSS</p>
      <fill style="width: 90%;"></fill>
    </bar>
    <bar>
      <p>Astro</p>
      <fill style="width: 75%;"></fill>
    </bar>
    <bar>
      <p>Python</p>
      <fill style="width: 70%;"></fill>
    </bar>
    <bar>
      <p>Luau</p>
      <fill style="width: 30%;"></fill>
    </bar>
    <bar>
      <p>C#</p>
      <fill style="width: 10%;"></fill>
    </bar>
  </div>

  <h1>What You Will See On My Blog</h1>
  <ul>
    <li>Photography</li>
    <li>IDE Setups/talk (Neovim)</li>
    <li>Coding Solutions (GitHub, Codeium, etc)</li>
    <li>Personal Projects</li>
    <li>Nerdy Stuff</li>
  </ul>
</Default>
